org.bukkit.event.inventory.InventoryInteractEvent

  • 使用InventoryInteractEvent的程序包 
    程序包 说明
    org.bukkit.event.inventory
    与物品栏操作相关的事件.

    • org.bukkit.event.inventory中InventoryInteractEvent的使用

      org.bukkit.event.inventory中InventoryInteractEvent的子类 
      限定符和类型 类和说明
      class  CraftItemEvent
      当一个物品被合成的时候触发这个事件.
      class  InventoryClickEvent
      当玩家点击物品栏中的格子时触发事件事件.
      class  InventoryCreativeEvent
      This event is called when a player in creative mode puts down or picks up an item in their inventory / hotbar and when they drop items from their Inventory while in creative mode.
      class  InventoryDragEvent
      This event is called when the player drags an item in their cursor across the inventory.
